title: Press machine for printing on leather US-618M

title_en: Press machine for printing on leather US-618M
short_description: We've all seen print on leather-bound notebooks and notepads. This US-618M device, performing a similar function, can perform its function in a size of 30*40 cm. The pressing pressure of the equipment is 500-800 kg, and the weight in the packed state is 190 kg.
short_description_uz: Barchamiz charm qoplamali daftar va bloknotlar ustidagi bosma yozularni ko'rganmiz. Xuddi shunday vazifani bajaruvchi ushbu US-618M uskuna 30*40 sm o'lchamda o'z vazifasini bajara oladi. Uskunaning presslash bosimi 500-800 kg ni tashkil etadi va qadoqlangan holatda vazni 190 kg dan iborat.
short_description_ru: Мы все видели печать на блокнотах и ​​блокнотах в кожаном переплете. Это устройство US-618M, выполняющее аналогичную функцию, может выполнять свою функцию размером 30*40 см. Давление прессования оборудования 500-800 кг, вес в упакованном виде 190 кг.

long_description:
We've all seen print on leather-bound notebooks and notepads. This US-618M device, performing a similar function, can perform its function in a size of 30*40 cm. The pressing pressure of the equipment is 500-800 kg, and the weight in the packed state is 190 kg. Another model of this equipment is shown below. They differ in price and parameters.

long_description_uz:
Barchamiz charm qoplamali daftar va bloknotlar ustidagi bosma yozularni ko'rganmiz. Xuddi shunday vazifani bajaruvchi ushbu US-618M uskuna 30*40 sm o'lchamda o'z vazifasini bajara oladi. Uskunaning presslash bosimi 500-800 kg ni tashkil etadi va qadoqlangan holatda vazni 190 kg dan iborat. Quyida ushbu uskunaning boshqa modeli ham aks etgan. Ular narx va parametrlarda bir-biridan farqlanadi.

 

Umumiy parametrlar
Model US-618M US-618D
Ishlov berish o'lchami (maks)............................................. 30*40 sm................................................................ 20*30 sm.....................................................................
Presslash bosimi 500-800 kg 300-500 kg
Uskunaning qadoqlangan vazni 190 kg 125 kg
